==Accidents and incidents==
On 5 March 1978 the Partenavian P.68 LN-MAD operated by Norving crashed at Falkefjell during approach to Vads<U+00F8> Airport. The crew of two and a passenger both survive, but the aircraft was written off.<ref>Melling: 154</ref>

